\par 
\par }\pard\plain \s15\ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f30\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\'93But you\rquote ll find no better honest purse peeler in all of Sigil. There\rquote 
