\par }{\line This Baatezu neighborhood, formerly situated between three portals to Baator, has seen itself shrink in recent years as two of its portals vanished during the Tempest of Doors. The population was also hit hard from the locals\rquote 
 heavy involvement in the rioting and open street warfare against the Tanar\rquote ri residents of the ward during that same period. 
