rs to share the beauty of their clockwork devices and machines, and half as a temple to order, or to the plane of Mechanus itself. The shop is widely trafficked by lawful bloods of all variety as well, and oddly enough is run not by a modron, but by a pri
me human and former Guvner named Saddam Hasan Ibn Arvalas, who claims to hail from Toril. Any manner of construct can be obtained within, though his waiting list for potential customers is long indeed. [Ask him about his mentor Trobriand back on Toril. 
